WEBVTT

00:09:27.674 --> 00:09:31.162
and the harms of prohibitionist policies.

00:09:31.162 --> 00:09:34.727
Now, with marijuana, that obviously means

00:09:34.727 --> 00:09:37.393
legally regulating and 
taxing it like alcohol.

00:09:37.393 --> 00:09:40.723
The benefits of doing so are
enormous, the risks minimal.

00:09:40.723 --> 00:09:43.434
Will more people use marijuana?

00:09:43.434 --> 00:09:47.405
Maybe, but it's not 
going to be young people,

00:09:47.405 --> 00:09:49.407
because it's not going to 
be legalized for them,

00:09:49.407 --> 00:09:51.218
and quite frankly, they already have

00:09:51.218 --> 00:09:53.254
the best access to marijuana.

00:09:53.254 --> 00:09:55.403
I think it's going to be older people.

00:09:55.403 --> 00:09:57.562
It's going to be people in their 40s and 60s

00:09:57.562 --> 00:10:01.208
and 80s who find they prefer a little marijuana